{"tid":1585800,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非國際主線] Freenix自由鳳凰正式誕生 #Birdfoldingchallenge","createTime":"2019-09-21T17:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T17:23:05.000Z","uid":51338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6ae859a56e0548a10f3062b4a457cd265ecf1143","tid":1585800,"uid":51338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:22:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">[和理非國際主線] Freenix自由鳳凰正式誕生 #birdfoldingchallenge</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VBJcWmi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVBJcWmi.jpg&h=7d84ffe9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong>*早前唔好意思，因為實在太難推post既關係，有TG友阻到大家*<br />\n</strong>最近和理非開始難以同抗爭活動有所同步，<br />\n而929全球反極權大遊行亦係時候需要更多宣傳工作。<br />\n外國朋友Enzo Mazak提出用#birdfoldingchallenge群體自發性推動既方式，<br />\n創造空間比本港和理非同外國人權關注人士重新加入香港抗爭運動。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">玩法好簡單:</span></strong><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uAvnzdo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuAvnzdo.png&h=060ec704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#birdfoldingchallenge以推廣人類三大普世價值之名(Freedom, Respect &amp; Love)，<br />\n號召全球力量對極權主義作出抵抗，<br />\n亦為國際線極為重要既929全球大遊行作出正面推廣和深度宣傳。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZnN1PKZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZnN1PKZ.jpg&h=4514779e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n*<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ztb6gmz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fztb6gmz.jpg&h=b09a4c7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>B.紙鳥TG團隊亦想幫香港區打造一隻 #Freebird 叫 #Freenix (Freedom+Phoenix)︰</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>#Freenix同香港人一樣：</strong></span><br />\n浴火不滅，傷癒重生<br />\n和勇自強，義無反顧<br />\n <br />\n*<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LDkrgnk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLDkrgnk.jpg&h=9653f3df&s={SIZE}\" /><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\nC. 除左呢條國際線，922沙田新城市仲會有特別企劃將大家手上既小Freebirds合體變大大鳥！呢個活動一野推出去比香港同世界知道同報導！</span></strong><br />\n <br />\n正面力量先能令抗爭活動夠走得更遠<br />\n全體參與，不分和勇，不分老幼，自己香港自己救！<br />\n <br />\n*<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Freenix - The Free Bird公海 - 摺完放入黎！</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/FreenixthefreebirdHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FFreenixthefreebirdHK&d=zoPJ6Qh4RBVN8MuZ9mClYmrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=db0ddd2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/FreenixthefreebirdHK</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n文宣、摺紙教學、摺紙pattern整合： （持續更新！）</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1eLY_GhZgSXg3_RjDY-hhv3B6vsJ--P9f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1eLY_GhZgSXg3_RjDY-hhv3B6vsJ--P9f&d=zoPJ6Qh4RBVN8MuZ9mClYmrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=ba245dcf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1eLY_GhZgSXg3_RjDY-hhv3B6vsJ--P9f</a><br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Freenix on Facebook</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/freenixstandforhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffreenixstandforhk&d=zoPJ6Qh4RBVN8MuZ9mClYmrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=8744f2eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/freenixstandforhk</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Enzo Mazak, #birdfoldingchallenge發起人</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EnzoMazak/status/1175236011246247938?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEnzoMazak%2Fstatus%2F1175236011246247938%3Fs%3D19&d=zoPJ6Qh4RBVN8MuZ9mClYmrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=0a544e29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEnzoMazak%2Fstatus%2F1175236011246247938%3Fs%